sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant UI as Dashboard UI
    participant API as /api/settings
    participant Store as Store
    participant Bot as ClankerBot

    UI->>API: PUT settings patch + expectedUpdatedAt
    API->>Store: patchSettingsWithVersion(patch, expectedUpdatedAt)
    Store->>Store: deepMerge + normalizeSettings
    alt settings changed since form load
        Store-->>API: conflict + latest settings snapshot
        API-->>UI: 409 conflict + latest settings
    else save succeeds
        Store->>Store: UPDATE settings WHERE updated_at = expectedUpdatedAt
        Store-->>API: saved settings + new updatedAt
        API->>Bot: applyRuntimeSettings(saved settings)
        alt runtime apply succeeds
            API-->>UI: 200 saved + applied=true
        else runtime apply fails
            API-->>UI: 200 saved + applied=false + applyError
        end
    end

    UI->>API: POST /api/settings/refresh
    API->>Store: getSettings()
    Store-->>API: latest saved config
    API->>Bot: applyRuntimeSettings(saved settings)
    API-->>UI: 200 active VC session sync result
